業發展既初期以戰養戰就岩架啦"},{"pid":"f6e6666f588ffb7096a2be3a1738dbf7d5795f48","tid":266473,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"我老婆人工都高過我，我就冇咩感覺，佢搵得多，我都鄧佢開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e96c0e26de1727067d9bad174e947065b2e9aa6","tid":266473,"uid":90634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老婆人工都高過我，我就冇咩感覺，佢搵得多，我都鄧佢開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b308047da14b38f4ec7d515bd06a659e532a02","tid":266473,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥老公咪要自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e046a5984417f18a51957cd008e205b757643936","tid":266473,"uid":91069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"我代入左個情境都有d唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更加唔開心係其實你個句係無心之失<br />\n<br />\n嗚呀 我個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea08f59f09f042261d6ff1f3431dbf84029e6385","tid":266473,"uid":120053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我代入左個情境都有d唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更加唔開心係其實你個句係無心之失<br />\n<br />\n嗚呀 我個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男朋友都俾我句無心之失搞到唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我先唔知可以做d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518a99c06d16863caeceabf336fffceb59c4219b","tid":266473,"uid":66712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017